<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ananchev</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f3f3f1;
            --paper: #ffffff;
            --ink: #111111;
            --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.16);
            --soft-line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
            --muted: #5d5d5d;
            --shadow: 16px 16px 0 #111111;
            font-family: "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100%;
            color: var(--ink);
            background-color: var(--bg);
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(to right, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 32px 32px;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 32px;
        }

        .page {
            width: min(1180px, 100%);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 28px;
            border: 2px solid var(--ink);
            background: var(--paper);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .topbar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 24px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .brand-mark {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border: 2px solid var(--ink);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .brand-copy {
            display: grid;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .brand-copy strong,
        .meta,
        .eyebrow,
        .tag,
        .card-label {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        }

        .brand-copy strong {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .brand-copy span,
        .meta,
        .lead,
        .card p,
        .status {
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .meta {
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 36px 0;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 11ch;
            font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
            line-height: 0.94;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        .lead {
            max-width: 34rem;
            margin: 28px 0 0;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 44px;
            padding: 0 18px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
            font-size: 0.76rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--ink);
            transition:
                transform 160ms ease,
                box-shadow 160ms ease,
                background-color 160ms ease,
                color 160ms ease;
        }

        .tag.inverse {
            background: var(--ink);
            color: var(--paper);
        }

        .tag.link {
            gap: 12px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tag.link::after {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .tag:hover {
            transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--ink);
        }

        .tag.inverse:hover {
            background: #2a2a2a;
        }

        .tag:focus-visible {
            outline: none;
            transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
            box-shadow:
                0 0 0 3px var(--paper),
                0 0 0 5px var(--ink),
                6px 6px 0 var(--ink);
        }

        .visual {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(6, 74px);
            gap: 12px;
            min-height: 100%;
        }

        .card {
            position: relative;
            padding: 18px;
            border: 2px solid var(--ink);
            background: var(--paper);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card.photo {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 14px;
        }

        .card.dark {
            background: var(--ink);
            color: var(--paper);
        }

        .card.dark p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 10px;
            border: 1px solid var(--soft-line);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .card.a {
            grid-column: 1 / 4;
            grid-row: 1 / 4;
        }

        .card.b {
            grid-column: 4 / 7;
            grid-row: 1 / 5;
        }

        .card.c {
            grid-column: 1 / 3;
            grid-row: 4 / 7;
        }

        .card.d {
            grid-column: 3 / 7;
            grid-row: 5 / 7;
        }

        .card.e {
            grid-column: 1 / 4;
            grid-row: 3 / 4;
        }

        .card-label {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-size: 0.74rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .card strong {
            display: block;
            max-width: 12ch;
            font-size: 1.55rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .card p {
            margin: 14px 0 0;
            max-width: 20ch;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .photo-frame {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            min-height: 100%;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 18px;
            border: 2px solid var(--ink);
            background:
                linear-gradient(to right, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08), transparent 58%),
                #efefec;
            background-size: 24px 24px, 24px 24px, auto, auto;
        }

        .photo-frame::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.18);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .photo-meta {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .photo-mark {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
            line-height: 0.9;
            letter-spacing: -0.07em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .photo-note {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 16ch;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.45;
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            padding-top: 28px;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
        }

        .info-box {
            min-height: 150px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
            background:
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.04), transparent 55%),
                var(--paper);
        }

        .info-box h2 {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        }

        .info-box p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .status {
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .page {
                padding: 22px;
                box-shadow: 10px 10px 0 #111111;
            }

            .hero,
            .footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .visual {
                grid-template-rows: repeat(6, 64px);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .topbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            h1 {
                max-width: none;
                font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 16vw, 4.5rem);
            }

            .visual {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                grid-template-rows: auto;
            }

            .card.a,
            .card.b,
            .card.c,
            .card.d,
            .card.e {
                grid-column: auto;
                grid-row: auto;
                min-height: 180px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="page">
        <header class="topbar">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="brand-mark">SF</div>
                <div class="brand-copy">
                    <strong>The Blog</strong>
                    <span>A space for solutions, clear and fast code</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta">Black / White / Geometry</div>
        </header>

        <section class="hero">
            <div class="copy">
                <p class="eyebrow">Welcome!</p>
                <h1>Hello. This is how it works faster.</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                   The goal of this blog is unlimited finding process how we and i could make 
                   the code faster and clearly. I will here write what i am thinking, what i am creating and dreaming
                </p>

                <div class="tags">
                    <a class="tag link" href="/resnt">Research and Tests</a>
                    <a class="tag link" href="/news">News</a>
                    <a class="tag link" href="/about">About me</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="visual">
                <article class="card a dark">
                    <span class="card-label">01</span>
                    <strong>New writing will appear here.</strong>
                    <p>Long-form posts, personal observations, and a calm publishing rhythm.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="card b photo">
                    <span class="card-label">02</span>
                    <div class="photo-frame">
                       <img src="/assets/me.jpg" />
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="card c">
                    <span class="card-label">03</span>
                    <strong>A place for news and short updates.</strong>
                    
                </article>

                <article class="card d">
                    <span class="card-label">04</span>
                    <strong>A clear beginning for the whole site.</strong>
                    <p>Later this can grow into an archive, article list, and a more detailed author page.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="card e dark">
                    <span class="card-label">05</span>
                    <strong>About me, in a simple and honest form.</strong>
                    <p>This website is meant to become personal, quiet, and very alive over time.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="footer-grid">
            <article class="info-box">
                <h2>Format</h2>
                <p>Long essays, short notes, personal announcements, and thoughts captured along the way.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="info-box">
                <h2>Approach</h2>
                <p>Careful typography, a simple composition, and a monochrome visual language.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="info-box">
                <h2>Now</h2>
                <p>For now this is a welcome page, but it already sets the tone for the blog that will follow.</p>
                <div class="status">First layout ready.</div>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
